name: Activation
text: Computes activation of selected layer for given input.

name: DeepLift
text: Implements DeepLIFT algorithm for the layer.

name: DeepLift Shap
text: Extends LayerDeepLift and DeepLiftShap algorithms and approximates SHAP values for given input layer.

name: Gradient X Activation
text: Computes element-wise product of gradient and activation for selected layer on given inputs.

name: Internal Influence
text: Computes internal influence by approximating the integral of gradients for a particular layer.

name: Integrated Gradients
text: A variant of Integrated Gradients that assigns an importance score to layer outputs

name: Conductance
text: Computes conductance with respect to the given layer. The returned output is in the shape of the layer’s output, showing the total conductance of each hidden layer neuron.
